<div style="font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;">
  <div
    style="
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
  "
  >
    <h1
      style="
      margin: 0;
      color: #282828;
      font-size: 25px;
      line-height: 200%;
      text-align: center;
      direction: ltr;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: normal;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    "
    >
      <strong>{{#if isLogin}}Login Verification{{else}}Email Verification{{/if}}</strong>
    </h1>
  </div>

  <div
    style="
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 150%;
    color: #000;
    direction: ltr;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
  "
  >
    <p style="margin: 0;">
      Hello
      <strong>{{userName}}</strong>, use this verification code below to complete your
      {{#if isLogin}}
        login
      {{else}}
        email verification and registration
      {{/if}}
      on
      <strong>Mentor App.</strong>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div
    style="
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 30px 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
  "
  >
    <div style="margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #666; font-weight: 500;">
      Your Verification Code
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <span
        style="
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 32px;
        color: #2563eb;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 6px;
        border: 2px dashed #2563eb;
        user-select: all;
        -webkit-user-select: all;
        -moz-user-select: all;
        -ms-user-select: all;
        cursor: text;
      "
      >{{verificationCode}}</span>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">üí° Tip: Click the code above to select and copy it</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    style="
    background: #fff3cd;
    border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
  "
  >
    <p
      style="
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #856404;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
    "
    >
      <strong>‚è∞ Important:</strong>
      This verification code will expire in 10 minutes. Please enter it in the
      app to complete your
      {{#if isLogin}}
        login.
      {{else}}
        registration.
      {{/if}}
    </p>
  </div>

  <div
    style="
    background: #e7f3ff;
    border: 1px solid #b3d9ff;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
  "
  >
    <p
      style="
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #0056b3;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
    "
    >
      <strong>üîí Security Tip:</strong>
      Never share this code with anyone. Mentor App will never ask for this code
      via phone, email, or text message.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div
    style="
    color: #000;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 120%;
    text-align: left;
    direction: ltr;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    margin: 20px 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
  "
  >
    <p style="margin: 0;">
      If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email or contact our support team.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div
    style="
    color: #000;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 150%;
    text-align: left;
    direction: ltr;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    margin: 10px 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
  "
  >
    <p style="margin: 0;">Warm regards,<br /><strong>Mentor App Team</strong></p>
  </div>
</div>